markets.title: Will Trump meet with Mohammed bin Salman before 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If the President of the United States meets Mohammed bin Salman in 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: A meeting will be included if the President and Mohammed bin Salman shake hands or speak to each other directly; the President merely attending the same conference or event as Mohammed bin Salman or being on a phone call with Mohammed bin Salman is not sufficient to resolve the market to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
